headline: UK Finance Watchdog to Ease Up on Firms Doing ‘the Right Thing’
summary: (Bloomberg) -- The UK’s top financial watchdog has promised a “less intensive approach” to firms whose intentions are pure, signaling a more pragmatic stance in a new five-year strategy that leans heavily into the government’s growth agenda.
